<notes>
Marian Hegemony infantry platoons consist of a 100-trooper Century comprised of ten 10-trooper contubernia or squads. Game play requires this to be broken down into units of 30 or fewer troopers, with the Duplus Contubernium being a two-squad (20 trooper) deployment and the Triplus Contubernium being a three-squad (30 trooper) deployment.
</notes>

